  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Hallis_Hornwood\" title=\"Hallis Hornwood\">Hallis Hornwood</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\"><img alt=\"House Hornwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/50px-House_Hornwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/75px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/100px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Halys Hornwood</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\"><img alt=\"House Hornwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/50px-House_Hornwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/75px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Hornwood.svg/100px-House_Hornwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Helman Tallhart Roose Bolton Halys Hornwood Medger Cerwyn by Amuelia.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png/300px-Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png/450px-Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png/600px-Helman_Tallhart_Roose_Bolton_Halys_Hornwood_Medger_Cerwyn_by_Amuelia.png 2x\" /></a><div><a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>, Halys Hornwood, and <a href=\"/index.php/Medger_Cerwyn\" title=\"Medger Cerwyn\">Medger Cerwyn</a> by Amuelia</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hornwood\" title=\"Lord of the Hornwood\">Lord of the Hornwood</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Green_Fork\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of the Green Fork\">Green Fork</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella Manderly</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daryn_Hornwood\" title=\"Daryn Hornwood\">Daryn Hornwood</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Larence_Snow\" title=\"Larence Snow\">Larence Snow</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Halys Hornwood</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> is Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Hornwood\" title=\"Hornwood\">Hornwood</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a>. He is the husband of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella Manderly</a> and the father of a trueborn heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Daryn_Hornwood\" title=\"Daryn Hornwood\">Daryn</a>, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">natural son</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Larence_Snow\" title=\"Larence Snow\">Larence Snow</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halys_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Halys is jovial and ever-obliging.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halys_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halys_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Halys goes to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> calls the banners. He gives gifts to Robb in hopes that he will give him leave to dam the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Knife\" title=\"White Knife\">White Knife</a>, hunting privileges north of a ridge, and a holdfast taken from his grandfather.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot53.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Hornwood is sent with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> when the northern army splits at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a>, and he is killed during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Green_Fork\" title=\"Battle on the Green Fork\">battle on the Green Fork</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Halys's son and heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Daryn_Hornwood\" title=\"Daryn Hornwood\">Daryn</a>, is slain at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_Whispering_Wood\" title=\"Battle in the Whispering Wood\">battle in the Whispering Wood</a> around the same time as Halys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halys_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella Hornwood</a> rules <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a> after the deaths of her husband and son.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halys_Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div 